https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m3Vyc2oRmrItN53fmiGOIsdLZ6u.jpg In the near future in the Asian city-state Sintawan, everyone's identity is recorded in the vast CyberLink. The only way around this is using illegal simulated identity implants (sims). A young bounty hunter who makes her living tracking sims, finds herself the unlikely ally of a police detective who suspects the CyberLink is being perverted for an insidious and deadly purpose Cyber Wars
